Description.Text: Hilton Dalian is 4 km from Dalian Train Station and shopping options at Renming Road. It is 14 km from Dalian Zhoushuizi Airport.

Located in Dalian?s East Harbor New Development Zone, the contemporary Hilton Dalian hotel is close to several luxury condominiums, office towers, a marina, a recreational boardwalk and Dalian?s new Convention Center.
Unwind in a spacious, air-conditioned Guest Room which features wireless internet access and a spacious bathroom.
Savour North-eastern Chinese cuisine Restaurant, Teppanyaki Genji-Japanese Restaurant,
Taste - All day dining, Drink - Lobby lounge and bar, Grab - Delicious snacks & coffee
